STATUS=ERROR|ADDIN=Power Pivot|MESSAGE=Failed after 5 retries|LAST_ERROR=1004 - Application-defined error

Đã bật sẵn:


STATUS=INFO|ADDIN=Microsoft Power Pivot for Excel|MESSAGE=Already ENABLED


